databaseQueries.query: SELECT `name` FROM `roles` inner join `role_user` on `roles`.`id` = `role_user`.`role_id` WHERE `role_user`.`user_id` = 6 and `role_user`.`user_type` = 'App\\Models\\User'

SELECT `name` FROM `permissions` inner join `permission_user` on `permissions`.`id` = `permission_user`.`permission_id` WHERE `permission_user`.`user_id` = 6 and `permission_user`.`user_type` = 'App\\Models\\User'
SELECT `display_name` FROM `roles` inner join `role_user` on `roles`.`id` = `role_user`.`role_id` WHERE `role_user`.`user_id` = 6 and `role_user`.`user_type` = 'App\\Models\\User'
